024 experience at your favourite ATKV Resort!\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ATKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bezuidenhout, the world No 46, is competing in his second Olympics, having finished tied 16th in Tokyo, where gold was won by American Xander Schauffele.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9898286953870812, \"rank\": 0.01014412475426109, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 756, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999990700989432, \"rank\": 6.058322280314245e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xander Schauffele\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xander_Schauffele\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latter is one of the favourites this week, having come into the event on the back of two Majors in 2024 so far.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section for free-to-read content  Both Bezuidenhout and Van Rooyen know that driving and putting well will be key this week to scoring well.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 1128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's always special to represent one's country at any level.\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Outside the Majors, this is one of the biggest stages to play.\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a great honour to have the chance to make South Africa proud both on and off the course.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999983482402967, \"rank\": 1.6517625113659367e-06, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I last played the course in 2016, which is a long time ago.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a good course from tee to green, and it's.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"set up tough.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You must stay on the fairways and find the greens.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The greens are big, so you need to attack the flag and set up a lot of chances to putt for birdies.\\\"\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van Rooyen is more familiar with the layout.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I played the French Open here a few times, it's a brilliant layout.\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is lots of trouble if you do not drive well, and there is a lot of water.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a typical ball-striking course, with lots of scoring opportunities.\\\"\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both players watched Tatjana Smith win gold in the women's 100m breaststroke and they have also seen a bit of gymnastics.\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are not staying in the Olympic athletes village, but have been to Team South Africa headquarters.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2090, \"end\": 2107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Team South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_baseball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The village left a lasting impression on them and Van Rooyen even took the opportunity to use the gym.\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is a little crowded though, not that easy to find a spot.\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then again, there are nearly 10 000 athletes staying in the village\\\" he laughed.\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow the golf at Le NationalLIVE  WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2407, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999987951589884, \"rank\": 1.2042360956116874e-06, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 2411, \"end\": 2413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.9960200367168281, \"rank\": 0.003985461800005966, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentenc